title: Benghazi committee Republicans must 'justify their own existence'
text: A House committee investigating the 2012 terrorist attacks in Benghazi, Libya, is losing credibility and Republicans on the panel now are under pressure to " justify their own existence, " White House press secretary Josh Earnest told reporters Monday.
